  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3635577">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3635577/" class="title-link">价值观的输出。</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3635577"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/xiexiong/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1430127-43.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/xiexiong/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">蟹熊</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-09-03"
      class="main-meta">2010-09-03 11:18:16</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3635577_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  讲地缘文化的部分非常中肯。 中国靠什么向国外输出价值观？是文化。 但是我们忘了中国除了文物，剩下的已经很少了。 何况现在的文物也在受到破坏。 我们如何输出我们没有的东西？  

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3635577_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3635577_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4499801">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
